{"tid":482354,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［冇圖] 冬天最撚怕呢樣野","createTime":"2017-11-28T05:44:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-28T06:27:22.000Z","uid":109703,"like":10,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3aedae92e27bc7895dd1059bfe9e162944ddf609","tid":482354,"uid":109703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T05:44:10.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我係怕凍唔怕熱嘅人 做運動都唔算大汗 冬天出街次次都著多人地幾件衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  之後比啲朋友恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我就中意夏天可以玩啲戶外/水上活動 雖然香港咁濕熱但我都頂得順 著衫又冇咁煩 冇咁腫 t-shirt短褲輕輕鬆鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n冬天沖完涼抹身又凍到仆街<br />\n最撚怕就係痾屎一野坐落個廁所板度凍到抽筋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人同我一樣中意夏天多過冬天?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中意夏天 痾屎唔怕凍 正<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  中意冬天 痾屎唔會痾到出汗 爽"},{"pid":"2e34fa50292bb2f640d5022d1654fcb09628a173","tid":482354,"uid":118623,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T05:45:00.000Z","msg":"到夏天你又話冬天好啲"},{"pid":"f7d75702fe35a812ece6154b77575ffb50c045db","tid":482354,"uid":33410,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T05:45:38.000Z","msg":"到夏天就會吹奏返冬天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf50d5f3374fd235dac0d5929af70507a23f26bf","tid":482354,"uid":38172,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T05:46:34.000Z","msg":"又投, on99"},{"pid":"3a2c6538060328c6531f461a3e1495f576ebc3bc","tid":482354,"uid":123456,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T05:47:37.000Z","msg":"段野好似廣告d 